uire artificial module/class-loading setup outside the supported library path.\n\nSo I would leave this one call site uncovered rather than add another brittle test that only exercises copied/shadowed classes or changes the runtime shape away from the tested artifact.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_080a077674b6d198016a2949e563188190947b3902cfd44bbe\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 4240, "output": 822, "cacheRead": 76288, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 81350, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781090775567, "responseId": "resp_080a077674b6d198016a2949d83efc819081b08dc7dac1cc2b"}}
